5000|$|In {{order for}} Leuchter or Rudolf to {{demonstrate}} the significance of their findings, {{it is necessary for}} them to prove the necessity of Prussian blue formation under the conditions that <b>the</b> homicidal <b>gas</b> <b>chambers</b> were operated. Showing that the delousing chambers have Prussian blue and that <b>the</b> homicidal <b>gas</b> <b>chambers</b> do not, proves nothing, if it cannot be shown that conditions in <b>the</b> <b>gas</b> <b>chambers</b> were such as to produce Prussian blue.|$|R
